YOU'RE HERE,

621
00:41:33,974 --> 00:41:36,477
JUST TO SEE YOU PERFORM
EVEN A SIMPLE SURGERY

622
00:41:36,977 --> 00:41:39,480
WOULD BE A GREAT THRILL
IN MY LIFE.

623
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,981
I'D REALLY RATHER NOT.

624
00:41:41,482 --> 00:41:42,983
I DON'T HAVE
MY INSTRUMENTS WITH ME.

625
00:41:42,983 --> 00:41:44,485
USE DR. HADLEY'S.

626
00:41:44,485 --> 00:41:48,489
THE KHAN'S BROTHER
IS BEING PREPPED NOW.

