SEVERE NERVE DAMAGE

633
00:42:05,506 --> 00:42:07,508
IN MY LEFT HAND.

634
00:42:07,508 --> 00:42:09,510
OH, MY GOD!

635
00:42:09,510 --> 00:42:11,512
YEAH. LOOK AT THAT.

636
00:42:11,512 --> 00:42:13,514
NO FEELING AT ALL.

637
00:42:13,514 --> 00:42:15,015
DEAD.

638
00:42:15,015 --> 00:42:17,017
HOW DID THAT HAPPEN?

639
00:42:17,017 --> 00:42:21,021
I WAS LIFTING
A CAR OFF A CHILD.

640
00:42:21,021 --> 00:42:23,023
IT WAS A BIG CADILLAC.

641
00:42:23,023 --> 00:42:25,025
I'M SO DISAPPOINTED.

642
00:42:25,025 --> 00:42:28,028
